column3: ACK b3926a2. Does not conflict with mine.\n

@laanwj I rebased this since you merged the prior PR, but then it occurred to me that maybe I shouldn't have b/c the ACK's don't line up.  Please let me know what you prefer for the future.\nAnyway, its the same text that was ACK'ed\n
@morcos If this was only a rebase, you can just do `git reset --hard b3926a2;git push <> -f` and GitHub will show it lined up. (b3926a2 is already rebased on the latest content)\n
